main event: A report describing an unusual visual phenomenon observed in the sky over Huntsville, Alabama on October 10, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as a blinking spot of light with trails,The observation lasted for about 5-10 seconds,The object appeared stationary at times before disappearing and reappearing,The document suggests a possible natural explanation involving jet exhaust,The report lacked sufficient information for further evaluation.
sighted object: blinking spot of light in the sky
witness description: A person with training in antiaircraft artillery and interests in optics and acoustics.
